{
  "application": "LSF",
  "description": "Submission script for LSF, to be invoked by blahpd server.",
  "usage": "lsf_submit.sh -c <command> [-i <stdin>] [-o <stdout>] [-e <stderr>] [-w working dir] [-- command's arguments]",
  "environment": {
    "lsf_confpath": "Path to lsf configuration file",
    "lsf_binpath": "Path to lsf binaries",
    "blah_libexec_directory": "Path to blahp libexec directory",
    "blah_sbin_directory": "Path to blahp sbin directory"
  },
  "requirements": {
    "binaries": [
      "bsub",
      "bkill",
      "lsid",
      "grep",
      "awk",
      "sed",
      "date",
      "find",
      "sleep",
      "echo",
      "rm"
    ],
    "files": [
      "lsf.conf",
      "blah_common_submit_functions.sh",
      "lsf_local_submit_attributes.sh"
    ]
  },
  "libraries": [
    "bls_BLClient"
  ]
}
